---
title: Katsu Chicken and Bacon Loaded Fries with cabbage slaw
description: These crispy chips are positively laden with delicious additions. Featuring golden fried chicken, zippy scallions, chilli for bite and a generous side of carrot and cabbage coleslaw, there's something for everyone in this exciting dish.
